trans_title: 蛋糕店老板 第二季
introduction: This season Buddy, his family and friends are back at Carlo's City Hall Bake Shop in Hoboken, New Jersey, and this Cake Boss has his work cut out for him. Watch as Buddy and his team of talented artists create amazing cakes for the local planetarium, a surprise proposal, a cake that talks, and many more. Stress runs high as business pours in and tempers flare. But at the end of the day this family's bond is the sweetest thing.
